  "1736290": {
    "name": "Crime O'Clock",
    "steam_appid": 1736290,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/58cdb4d2a55ca8edb4b750ff2d971073.webp?t=1712675428\" width=600 height=49 /></span> 。<br>警报! 警报!<br>时空连续体处于危险之中! <br>在犯罪发生之前预防犯罪! 现在是犯罪时刻!<br>通过时间和不断变化的地图来调查案件，揭开一个多eras联系的故事。你是否有足够的观察力来解开这些谜团？犯罪不等人!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/85d1cb317f07d5f2133fd60844dedf67.poster.avif?t=1712675428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/85d1cb317f07d5f2133fd60844dedf67.webm?t=1712675428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/85d1cb317f07d5f2133fd60844dedf67.mp4?t=1712675428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/d2d51791837eaec190ecc19abf8ca6fa.webp?t=1712675428\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br>作为一个时间侦探，你的工作是通过时间来解决那些本不应该发生的犯罪！每张地图都有<strong>多个时间点。<br>每张地图都有<strong>多个时间标记</strong>可供访问和使用，以解决不同的黑客攻击、谋杀、盗窃等案件。<br>但几个世纪以来，一个共同的奇怪事件正在发展......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/052c1e91dae5cb7b2d9ee5ccfaadd3fb.poster.avif?t=1712675428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/052c1e91dae5cb7b2d9ee5ccfaadd3fb.webm?t=1712675428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/052c1e91dae5cb7b2d9ee5ccfaadd3fb.mp4?t=1712675428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/160a47439e8171d17a8da4e55846d82b.webp?t=1712675428\" width=600 height=60 /></span> 。<br>有什么东西或人在试图扰乱时间，找到它! <br>一张<strong>巨大</strong>的每个时代的可缩放地图是推理和寻找线索的游戏场地。<br><strong>你</strong>必须用<strong>演绎法</strong>进行，以结合缺失的碎片。<br>通过解决案件，<strong>地图变化</strong>和<strong>新的冒险</strong>被解锁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/88aa5d9f0f8b710b3497c814f8e9ca06.poster.avif?t=1712675428\" width=600 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/88aa5d9f0f8b710b3497c814f8e9ca06.webm?t=1712675428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/88aa5d9f0f8b710b3497c814f8e9ca06.mp4?t=1712675428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/855ba2552a3f1902a8313c6461f1c946.webp?t=1712675428\" width=606 height=48 /></span> <br>正如你所看到的，这是一个<strong>点和点击</strong>的游戏；你唯一需要的技能是你的全功能的大脑来解除犯罪计划！你的工作不会是孤独的。<br>你在工作中不会孤单。EVE，一个先进的人工智能，将帮助你，提供指导和工具。<br>使用EVE的系统，你有新的方法来寻找线索和证据：演绎环节与动作和拼图机制交替进行，以获得完整的用户体验。<br>在你的冒险过程中，EVE将升级其系统，解锁新功能......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/7b850f4c389f882b6d7b50c5b602c408.poster.avif?t=1712675428\" width=600 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/7b850f4c389f882b6d7b50c5b602c408.webm?t=1712675428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/7b850f4c389f882b6d7b50c5b602c408.mp4?t=1712675428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/6e75c62bc6d05a3ccb0d782e0945cf5f.webp?t=1712675428\" width=600 height=51 /></span> <br>在调查过程中，你将探索五个不同的时代。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>蒸汽时代：自动装置、疯狂发明和哥特秘事丛生的年代<br></li><li>亚特兰提斯时代：魔力水晶和和平乌托邦文明的年代。<br></li><li>信息时代：以开发者家乡意大利米兰为真实背景的年代。这座城市中集聚了一些最具标志性的建筑和艺术品，如米兰大教堂、斯福尔扎城堡、最后的晚餐等等！<br></li><li>失落的时代--时间的沙子隐藏着神秘和技术的奇迹。<br></li><li>霓虹时代--明亮的灯光、无情的社会和地下的斗争--科技先行</li></ul><br><br>【更多内容！】<br><br>摇摆故事模式为《Crime O'Clock》带来了一种全新且不同的玩法。自由移动，试着重建30多个角色穿越10个时间刻度的旅程。你甚至可能会认出一些角色...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/4e169ccefad8678281de89ea2418bdb0.avif?t=1712675428\" width=600 height=145 /></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1712675428\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1712675428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736290/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1712675428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong>",
